<div class="rr-settings-section">

!! Profiles

Discovery profiles (JSON array). Each profile defines a directory structure to scan for binary files. Changes require a server restart.

<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/scattered-binaries/profiles" tag="textarea" class="rr-input" rows="12"/>

!! Profile Fields

|!Field |!Description |!Example |
|`basePath` |Directory to scan (relative to wiki root) |`tiddlers/tender` |
|`dirPattern` |Regex for subdirectory names to match |`^#` (matches `#512`, `#516`) |
|`subFolder` |Subfolder within matched dirs containing binaries |`documents` |
|`routePrefix` |HTTP route prefix for serving files |`/tender-docs` |
|`tiddlerPrefix` |Tiddler title prefix |`tender` |
|`tag` |Tag applied to created tiddlers |`tender-source-document` |

</div>
